    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="在安卓里，界面需要频繁的变化，需要用handler来刷新界面才能稳定运行。下面就是我使用的心得笔记。"><a href="#在安卓里，界面需要频繁的变化，需要用handler来刷新界面才能稳定运行。下面就是我使用的心得笔记。" class="headerlink" title="在安卓里，界面需要频繁的变化，需要用handler来刷新界面才能稳定运行。下面就是我使用的心得笔记。"></a>在安卓里，界面需要频繁的变化，需要用handler来刷新界面才能稳定运行。下面就是我使用的心得笔记。</h3><ul><li>在刷新Activity添加Handler</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">// 刷新界面</div><div class="line">private Handler mHandler = new <span class="function"><span class="title">Handler</span></span>() &#123;</div><div class="line">public void handleMessage(Message msg) &#123;</div><div class="line">super.handleMessage(msg);</div><div class="line">String str = (String) msg.obj;</div><div class="line">//根据获取的消息来执行刷新任务</div><div class="line">Log.e(<span class="string">"获取的消息"</span>,<span class="string">"str"</span>);</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">&#125;;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><a id="more"></a><ul><li>同Activity中调用Handler</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">new <span class="function"><span class="title">Thread</span></span>() &#123;</div><div class="line">public void <span class="function"><span class="title">run</span></span>() &#123;</div><div class="line">try &#123;</div><div class="line">String str=<span class="string">"要发送的消息"</span>;</div><div class="line">Message msg = Message.obtain();</div><div class="line">msg.obj = str;</div><div class="line">mHandler.sendMessage(msg);</div><div class="line">&#125; catch (InterruptedException e) &#123;</div><div class="line">e.printStackTrace();</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">&#125;.start();</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>非Activity页面调用Handler</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">public class UseHandler&#123; </div><div class="line">private EditText et;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">// 刷新界面</div><div class="line">private Handler mHandler = new <span class="function"><span class="title">Handler</span></span>() &#123;</div><div class="line">public void handleMessage(Message msg) &#123;</div><div class="line">super.handleMessage(msg);</div><div class="line">et.setText((String) msg.obj);</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">&#125;;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">//传入Activity显示组件</div><div class="line">public WeatherAPI(EditText et) &#123;</div><div class="line">this.et=et;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">//线程实现消息传递</div><div class="line">new <span class="function"><span class="title">Thread</span></span>()&#123;</div><div class="line">public void <span class="function"><span class="title">run</span></span>()&#123;</div><div class="line">String msg = <span class="string">"显示的文字"</span>;</div><div class="line">Message message = Message.obtain();</div><div class="line">message.obj = msg;</div><div class="line">mHandler.sendMessage(message);</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">&#125;.start();</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
